snippet.title: Disney Channel presents Superbia!
snippet.description:
In Superbia, you are in control, your place, your friends, your rules! Why not decorate your own place, make your own Ice Cream Sundaes, pick up new clothes or just chill out in your favourite Disney Channel area! 

Come and hang out in Disney's Superbia, head to disneychannel.co.uk/superbia!
